dMain editor functions
ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄa

    c[main functions]a
    bF1a       - help
    bF2a       - save
    bF3a       - save and show in graphics !
    bF4a       - save and run source editor
    bF5a       - change colour from cursor
    bF6a       - change font from cursor
    bShift F6a - change font from cursor to one of fonts already used on page
    bCtrl F6a  - replace all occurrences of one font with a different font
    bF7a       - create link to some other page or script
                After selecting some page, you'll get page.
                Fill a reference (the word that will be underlined)
                to get a valid link like: referencepage.
    bShift F7a - link to other page/picture/anim/sample/module/script
    bF8a       - insert a picture or an animation
    bShift F8a - insert a picture or an animation as link
                to other page/picture/animation...
    bF10a      - insert object (but usually more suitable is the way with F7)
    bF12,Alt-Xa- quit editor
    bTABa      - one TAB on line beginning aligns text to left
                two TABs on line beginning shifts text as new paragraph
                TABs inside text has no meaning

    c[layers]a
    bF9a       - split layer under cursor
    bShift F9a - merge this and previous layer into one, inverse to F9
    bAlt 1..9a - jump to layer 1..9
    bdragging with left buttona             - move whole layer
    bhorizontal dragging with right buttona - change layer width
    bvertical dragging with right buttona   - rehook layer to another layer


dCommon functions
ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄa

    c[cursor movement]a
    barrowsa               - move cursor left/right/up/down
    bCtrl arrowsa          - jump a word left/right
    bHomea                 - to the begin of line
    bEnda                  - to the end of line
    bPageUpa               - 20 rows up
    bPageDowna             - 20 rows down
    bCtrl Homea            - to the begin of layer
    bCtrl Enda             - to the end of layer
    bCtrl PageUpa          - to the begin of file
    bCtrl PageDowna        - to the end of file
    bclicking left buttona - position cursor

    c[deleting/writing]a
    bDeletea               - delete char under cursor
    bBackspacea            - delete char before cursor
    bCtrl Ya               - delete one row
                           if picture starts at next line, it's also deleted
    bCtrl Ta               - delete from cursor to begin of next word
    bInserta               - insert a new row

    c[blocks]a
    bShift [move cursor]a  - MARK block
    bShift Deletea         - CUT block to memory
    bShift Inserta         - PASTE block from memory
    bCtrl Inserta          - COPY block to memory
    bCtrl Deletea          - DELETE block

    c[others]a
    bclicking right buttona- menu (also bAlt-Sa menu, bAlt-Da repeats last selection)
    bEsca                  - leave page


